@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_etipsk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.93
    v0 = wp.cos(v2)
    tmp = 0.42
    v1 = ((0.22 - v1) * (tmp * wp.cos(v2 + 0.49)))
    tmp = (0.09 / v0)
    v1 = (v2 + ((v2 + 0.38 - v1 + 0.72) - (v0 + 0.15 - v0 + 0.06)))
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.80) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.48)))
    v0 = 0.76
    data[tid] = v0
